https://learn.microsoft.com/en-gb/training/modules/security-copilot-getting-started/?source=docs

Organizations face unprecedented challenges, in the rapidly evolving digital landscape, such as increasingly sophisticated cyber threats and a significant talent shortage in cybersecurity. Microsoft Copilot for Security is a cloud-based, AI-powered security analysis tool that is designed to address these challenges. 
It enables analysts to process security signals and respond to threats at a machine speed that far surpasses human capabilities, thus revolutionizing the way organizations approach cybersecurity.
